[Name] beep
[Summary] Play simple tunes using PC system speaker
[License] GNU General Public License (GPL) V2
[Description] This program isn't supposed to be anything stupendous, it's just supposed to get the job done.  Its intended purpose in life is to live inside shell/perl scripts, and allow a little more granularity than you get with the default terminal bell.
[Homepage] http://johnath.com/beep/
